# Editorial rules (directory + guides)

## Directory listings (`src/data/businesses.js`)

- Facts from verified public sources only. Unknown field → `null` (row omitted).
- **Contact:** website, email, WhatsApp and LINE — not published landline phones, except verified numbers on 24-hour emergency vet listings.
- Verdicts (`recommend` / `ok` / `avoid`) only after anonymous visit with bill paid in full.
- Verdict scope: business experience only — never veterinary medical quality.
- No paid placements, sponsored tags, or affiliate links.

## Guides

- Orientation, not vet advice. Include verify-with-official-source blocks on import/export.
- Date-stamp every page (`updated: "YYYY-MM-DD"`).
- Match patterns in `src/guidekit.js` and sibling pages in the same cluster.

## Disclaimer

Every page carries: editorial/informational only, not veterinary advice.
